% GAMMACORRECTIONTABLEGLOBALS - Defines globals for gamma correction%% NewStim allows one to specify a gamma-correction table to correct for% luminance non-linearities in monitors.  The following global variables% specify parameters for gamma-correction.%% GammaCorrectionEnable     : 0/1 use gamma correction?% GammaCorrectionTable      : Table of gamma correction values%% See also:  LoadGammaCorrectionTable, ApplyGammaCorrectionglobal GammaCorrectionEnable GammaCorrectionTable